Coding Conventions for SOAPUI/READY API Projects

1. Following strict naming conventions
	In Request Names
	In property Names
	In Groovy Scripts
	Cookie Names
	
2. Organisaing variavles:
	@Project level
	@TestSuite level
	@TestCase level

3. Keeping Logging Statements to make it easy for debugging
		Phase wise log statements
		Final log statement

4. Null checks in groovy bscripts

5. Retry logics with
		max retry count
		max retry timeout

6. Keeping neat interface definitions
